text: Hyannis Port (or Hyannisport) is a small residential village located in Barnstable, Massachusetts, United States. It is a summer community on Hyannis Harbor, 1.4 miles to the south-southwest of Hyannis. Hyannis Port is the location of the Kennedy Compound and other Kennedy family residences. ==References== Category:Villages in Massachusetts
